{"tid":669106,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗令我太感動","createTime":"2018-05-18T08:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T10:23:37.000Z","uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"acb872164952ebc18c10f0f166bb3a96cc28fed5","tid":669106,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"C朗撐歌手老友助癌病兒童<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=sJYsVS0QOKf%2B1QUKuGT5cqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=3ab7ea25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西班牙唱作歌手Enrique Iglesias將會捐出7%的演唱會利潤，來幫助西班牙的癌病兒童，基斯坦奴朗拿度對好友這個決定大表支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）在twitter說：「非常高興地宣佈，我的朋友Enrique Iglesias將會把里斯本演唱會所得的7%利潤捐給IPO（位於里斯本的癌症治療中心）。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nC朗一向<span style=\"color: red;\">善心爆棚</span>，IPO正是其中一間他有份伸出援手協助的機構之一，老友Enrique Iglesias仿傚他做出如此有善心的動作，難怪C朗表現如此雀躍。<span style=\"color: red;\">C朗球場以外被冠以「慈善球王」外號，亦絕非浪得虛名</span>，據西班牙網站《telecinco》報道，C朗早前就曾為家鄉葡萄牙一名患癌男童，<span style=\"color: red;\">支付了所有的醫療費用。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC朗好友Enrique Iglesias同樣來頭不少，他在拉丁樂壇是一位非常成功的唱作歌手，於美國和拉丁美洲廣受歡迎，其專輯於全球銷量超過6千萬張，當中2張更在最受歡迎Billboard 100排行榜上，獲得第1和第3名。"},{"pid":"f1b4bb51fe2bd5039ef9200972823a196064f4f7","tid":669106,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"c朗真係好照顧土方蛇"},{"pid":"5c534ae27179a7eb6fae3b18a1be2e8be8dfaedb","tid":669106,"uid":366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"所以政府捉佢逃稅真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333340bf5d54ffb94f9364ac175b719b42b14f19","tid":669106,"uid":23385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1b4bb51fe2bd5039ef920097